```plantuml
@startuml

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam style strictuml

note top of Invoker : 调用者持有命令对象，\n并在某刻调用execute()
note top of Command : 调用命令对象的execute()\n就可以让接收者进行动作
note right of Client : 这个客户负责创建一个\nConcreteCommand，并\n设置其接收者
note left of ConcreteCommand : 定义了动作和接收者之间\n的绑定关系，调用者只需\n要调用execute()就可以\n发出请求
note right of Receiver : 接收者知道如何实现这个请求

interface Invoker {
}

interface Command {
  execute()
  undo()
}

interface Client {
}

class ConcreteCommand {
  execute()
  undo()
}

interface Receiver {
  action()
}

Invoker --> Command
Client --> ConcreteCommand
Client --> Receiver
Command <|.. ConcreteCommand
ConcreteCommand <-- Receiver

@enduml
```
